title: Leading the Way: 100 Years of the Tararua Tramping Club – Shaun Barnett & Chris Maclean
description: Barnett and Maclean with their wealth of experience in this area have produced a magnificent book to celebrate 100 years of the club. Using extensive written and visual archives this book celebrates the adventures, the ‘family’ of members and their contribution to the support and appreciation of our unique environment.
